00:09:06,557 --> 00:09:07,434
S.S.

205
00:09:07,434 --> 00:09:08,799
 S.S.-vakh, ye?

206
00:09:08,799 --> 00:09:09,688
ye.

207
00:09:09,688 --> 00:09:12,452
un ver flegt aykh firn oyf der arbet? ver flegt aykh bagleytn?

208
00:09:12,452 --> 00:09:16,031
bagleytn iz oykh di S.S. merstn teyl.

209
00:09:16,031 --> 00:09:19,837
efsher gedenkt ir fun lager bizn arbets-ort

210
00:09:19,837 --> 00:09:22,908
fun MALKEN, hot ir gedarft lang geyn?

211
00:09:22,908 --> 00:09:24,030
lang.

212
00:09:24,030 --> 00:09:25,188
vifl umgefer tsayt?

213
00:09:25,188 --> 00:09:28,855
nu? mistomen a

