neyn. keyn zakh vel ikh ir nit gebn, un keyn ergets loz ikh ir nit arayn.

592
00:27:21,157 --> 00:27:23,718
in dr'erd far ir an ort!" zogt er.

593
00:27:23,718 --> 00:27:29,455
"az zi" zogt er "ken zikh azoy bageyn mit aykh, un du heyst ir nor" zogt er "araynlozn?"

594
00:27:29,455 --> 00:27:32,982
un er hot ir nit arayngelozt. zog ikh tsu ir "zest" zog ikh ir

595
00:27:32,982 --> 00:27:34,876
"az du voltst mir arayngelozn.

596
00:27:34,876 --> 00:27:37,824
voltstu dokh aleyn geven, un ikh volt dir keyn zakh nit geton.

597
00:27:37,824 --> 00:27:40,385
"un itster" zog ikh "hob ikh gemuzt &lt;zogn&gt; oyf dir.

598
00:27:40,385 --> 00:27:43,192
ver du bist" zog ikh "vayl ikh bin dokh azoy krank" zog ikh.

599
00:27:43,192 --> 00:27:45,508
"ikh ken dokh nit geyn.

600
00:27:45,508 --> 00:27:48,631
ot" zog ikh "hostu itster. veyst? undzer tam."

601
00:27:48,631 --> 00:27:50,701
un az ir zayt geven krank

602
00:27:50,701 --> 00:27:53,753
ir hot gele- ir hot gelegn dray vokhn in di shtibele?

603
00:27:53,753 --> 00:27:54,280
ya.

604
00:27:54,280 --> 00:27:55,859
ver hot aykh oyfgepast?

605
00:27:55,852 --> 00:27:59,156
ver hot mir oyfgepast? mayn shviger mit mayn shvegerin. un di,

606
00:27:58,613 --> 00:27:59,332
un zey

607
00:27:59,332 --> 00:28:01,428
un di rusn flegn undz altsding brengen.

608
00:28:00,876 --> 00:28:02,560
un zey hobn gelebt tsuzamen mit aykh?

609
00:28:02,560 --> 00:28:03,773
di rusn? neyn.

610
00:28:03,174 --> 00:28:05,416
neyn, neyn, ayer sh- ayer shviger.

611
00:28:04,911 --> 00:28:06,806
ya, ya, ya, ya.

612
00:28:06,806 --> 00:28:08,869
iz ir hot gelebt, in eyn tsimer, ye?

613
00:28:08,315 --> 00:28:10,385
zaynen geven mit mir tsuzamen, ye.

614
00:28:10,385 --> 00:28:12,420
un ir hot gedarft hobn refues

615
00:28:12,420 --> 00:28:16,069
alts hobn gebrakht di rusn. mir hobn dokh keyn gelt nit gehat.

616
00:28:16,332 --> 00:28:17,508
di rusn hobn alts gebrakht.

617
00:28:17,508 --> 00:28:20,797
un der dokter, der rusisher militerisher dokter flegt kumen tsu aykh?

618
00:28:20,122 --> 00:28:23,227
iz gekumen a dokter on gelt, on keyn zakh.

619
00:28:23,227 --> 00:28:24,981
er iz geven a militer-man?

620
00:28:24,981 --> 00:28:27,034
a froy iz gekumen a dokter.

621
00:28:27,034 --> 00:28:30,122
mistome iz zi geven a- in militer.

622
00:28:30,122 --> 00:28:35,095
zi flegt tsu aykh kumen, zi flegt ey- nor eyn mol, eyn mol, zi hot eyn mol geven bay aykh, tsu flegt zi

623
00:28:34,525 --> 00:28:35,771
etlekhe mol iz zi geven.

624
00:28:35,771 --> 00:28:39,315
etlekhe mol, ye? un vos flegt zi aykh brengen?

625
00:28:39,315 --> 00:28:42,771
refues velkhe m'hot gedarft. ikh gedenk shoyn nit velkhe.

626
00:28:42,771 --> 00:28:46,385
nor zi flegt altsding brengen, un esn flegt zi undz brengen.

627
00:28:46,385 --> 00:28:48,321
un ir hot zikh a bisl opgekhapt dan.

628
00:28:48,139 --> 00:28:51,999
nu, farshteyt zikh. zey hobn undz nit gelozn laydn.

